teetime.framework

Class Stage

  • java.lang.Object
    • teetime.framework.Stage
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractStage

    public abstract class Stage
extends Object
    Represents a minimal Stage, with some pre-defined methods. Implemented stages need to adapt all abstract methods with own implementations.

      protected org.slf4j.Logger logger

      The owning thread of this stage if this stage is directly executed by a AbstractRunnableStage, null otherwise.
